            </a>
            <div class="text-teal-500">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/chadmcelligott/" title="Connect on LinkedIn">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="currentColor" class="inline-block mx-4" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
